### admin login
POST http://localhost:4000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email":"admin@gmail.com",
    "password":"admin123"
}


### admin logout
GET http://localhost:4000/auth/logout



### read all users & authors(email for deactivating)
GET http://localhost:4000/admin-api/users

### block or activate user & author
PUT http://localhost:4000/admin-api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userId":"69b3ab522918a77cfbfaf4c8"
}